==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dispauper
<hw>Dis*pau"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deprive of
the claim of a pauper to public support; to deprive of the privilege of
suing <xex>in forma pauperis</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dispauperize</ent>⟦br⟧
